flowchart LR
    subgraph build [Build Stage]
        Checkout[Checkout code] --> Install[Install deps]
        Install --> Compile[Compile]
    end
    subgraph test [Test Stage]
        Compile --> Lint[Lint]
        Lint --> UnitTests[Unit tests]
        UnitTests --> IntegrationTests[Integration tests]
    end
    subgraph deploy [Deploy Stage]
        IntegrationTests --> Package[Package]
        Package --> Push[Push image]
        Push --> Release{Release?}
        Release -->|Yes| Deploy[Deploy to prod]
        Release -->|No| End[Done]
        Deploy --> End
    end
